---
import { SOCIAL, AUTHOR } from '../../site.config';
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 pt-12 pb-8 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-12">
  <h1 class="sr-only">{AUTHOR.name} â€” {AUTHOR.jobTitle}</h1>
  <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
    <a
      href="/about"
      aria-label={`About ${AUTHOR.name}`}
      class="group mx-auto mb-6 block w-fit rounded-full ring-2 ring-transparent transition-all duration-300 hover:ring-accent-600/50 sm:float-left sm:mb-4 sm:mr-6"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/profile.jpg"
        alt={AUTHOR.name}
        width="160"
        height="160"
        class="h-32 w-32 rounded-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 sm:h-40 sm:w-40"
      />
    </a>
    <p class="text-center sm:text-left">
      Senior iOS Engineer with 12+ years of experience building high-performance, scalable mobile applications. Expert in Swift, SwiftUI, Combine, and complex systems architecture, with a proven track record in fintech high-load trading apps, hardware integrations (BLE/IoT), and leading migrations to modern declarative architectures.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center sm:text-left">
      Co-Founder of Your Accessible Flight, where I'm developing an AI-powered platform to make air travel barrier-free for people with disabilities, featuring mobility aid verification, accessibility planning, and innovative tools like RAG-based chat assistants and computer vision for equipment analysis.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center sm:text-left">
      Passionate about pushing boundaries in AI and Robotics - not just using existing APIs, but creating entirely new, proactive solutions that evolve with users and truly transform experiences.
